Download TIGER shapes for Places

Source: R/places.R
tt_places.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Places

Usage

tt_places(state, year = 2021)

Arguments

state

FIPs, postal codes, or full name of states.

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_places('DE')
